e change&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://opentofu.org/&#34;&gt;OpenTofu&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;re enjoying the podcast, please remember to subscribe and share this episode with your friends and colleagues!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
